 `ConfigOptionSet` is the new top-level class for classes such as `BlobServerOptions` or `ExecutionConfigOptions`. It enables accessing all defined options and cross-option validation. We can provide a static utility function that instantiates the set and calls `validate(conf)` for eager set validation. ` ` /** Class for a set of {@link ConfigOption}s. */
